Do's
Do use privacy settings to control who sees your personal posts.
Do curate a professional LinkedIn profile for networking.
Do verify the accuracy of information before sharing.
Do use a professional profile picture for career-related accounts.
Do network by sharing insightful industry-related content.

Dont's
Do's,Don'ts
Don't post confidential information about college projects or code.
Don't engage in public arguments or use offensive language.
Don't tag others in photos without their explicit permission.
Don't post content that violates campus conduct policies.
Don't overshare personal grievances regarding faculty or peers.